                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1904-08-25">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 25, 1904</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>American cruiser <hi rend="italic">Buffalo</hi> ordered patrol waters Commander
                    Islands.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Adee.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
